name: Ottez United Ticket - With Love To Ukraine
description:
All ticket sales for this specific ticket will be going to Ukraine Fund, with five percent set to the collab contract team. Let's love one anotter and bring peace on Earth. 

Ottez holders can contact @YinYangYoeshi on Monday Feb. 28th, 2022 to have their Ottez put into the event/meme.

In the spirit of this idea, feel free to trade this NFT after the event. All royalties will also go to the Ukraine fund and devs of this collab contract. Non Ottez holders are also welcome to participate but will not be able to be "in the scene".
